<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.6">
<l>uruvuṭai yāriḷai yārkaṇallā rōttuval lārkaḷaik koṇṭuvaikal</l>
<l>teruviṭai yetirkoṇṭu paṅkuṉināṟ ṟiruntavē nōṟkiṉṟēṉ kāmatēvā</l>
<l>karuvuṭai mukilvaṇṇaṉ kāyāvaṇṇaṉ karuviḷai pōlvaṇṇaṉ kamalavaṇṇat</l>
<l>tiruvuṭai mukattiṉiṟ ṟirukkaṇkaḷāṟ ṟiruntavē nōkkeṉak karuḷukaṇṭay.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O lord Kāma! Everyday during the Paṅkuṉi-month, I am practising austerities</l>
<l rend="indent">in a worthy way,</l>
<l>going forward in the street, taking [with me] people who are beautiful, young, good,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] capable in [the art of] lovemaking.</l>
<l>Look, graciously glance [at me] so that He of the hue of pregnant clouds,</l>
<l>of ironwood flowers, He of the hue akin to the mussel-shell creeper</l>
<l>should look [at me] in a perfect way with the sacred eyes on the lustrous, lotus-hued face.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
